name: "Jaipur" Tara Lea Smith Statement Couture Earrings
description:
My name is Tara Lea Smith and I am a jewelry artist based out of Cincinnati, Ohio. Art is my passion, and I have been creative ever since my childhood. I love learning new art forms and experimenting with different materials. Designing jewelry is a hobby that my grandmother and I shared. We would often create jewelry together and she inspired me to be a jewelry artist.

I graduated from Miami University with a B.S. in Art Education and an academic minor in Art History in 2009. I am a licensed Art Teacher for the State of Ohio and Kentucky. I love teaching art and watching children learn and develop by expressing themselves through what they create.
